        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>At SwiftShip Logistics, we value your trust and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our delivery services and mobile application (the "App").</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our services or app, we may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, address, email address, phone number, and delivery details.</li>
            <li><strong>App Usage Data:</strong> Device information, app interactions, and location data (if enabled).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We only use your information for work-related purposes, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Processing and delivering your packages.</li>
            <li>Communicating with you about your orders or services.</li>
            <li>Improving our app and services to enhance your experience.</li>
            <li>Ensuring the security of your account and our operations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Completing your delivery (e.g., sharing details with couriers).</li>
            <li>Complying with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no system is entirely secure, and we encourage you to use strong passwords and report any suspicious activity.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access the information we have about you.</li>
            <li>Request corrections to inaccurate or incomplete information.</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data, subject to legal or operational requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Retention of Information</h2>
        <p>We retain your data only as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in this policy, comply with legal obligations, or resolve disputes.</p>

        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated through the app or via email.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: Swiftship736@gmail.com</li>
            <li>Phone: 0500464012</li>
        </ul>
